{
    "key": 14702,
    "messages": [
        {
            "id": "EternaGym_Text_GardeniaIntro",
            "en_US": [
                "You kept me waiting!\r",
                "I\u2019m Eterna\u2019s Gym Leader, Gardenia,\n",
                "the Grass-type master!\r",
                "When I first saw you, I was convinced\n",
                "you\u2019d find your way to me.\r",
                "My hunch was right on the money.\n",
                "You have a winning aura about you.\r",
                "So, anyway, this will be fun.\n",
                "Let\u2019s have our battle!\r"
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": "EternaGym_Text_BeatGardenia",
            "en_US": [
                "I might\u2019ve said it before, but you\u2019re\n",
                "really tough!\r",
                "Wasn\u2019t it hard for you to raise your\n",
                "Pok\u00e9mon to be so good?\r",
                "I guess that\u2019s a measure of how much\n",
                "you love your Pok\u00e9mon.\r",
                "In recognition of that, I proudly\n",
                "grant you this!\r"
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": "EternaGym_Text_GardeniaReceiveForestBadge",
            "en_US": [
                "{STRVAR_1 3, 0, 0} received the\n",
                "Forest Badge from Gardenia!"
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": "EternaGym_Text_GardeniaExplainForestBadge",
            "en_US": [
                "With the Forest Badge, your Pok\u00e9mon\n",
                "can use the hidden move Cut outside\f",
                "of battle.\r",
                "Now that you have two Gym Badges,\n",
                "all Pok\u00e9mon you received in trades\f",
                "will obey you up to Lv. 30.\r",
                "I\u2019ve also got something else.\n",
                "It\u2019s a gift from me!\r"
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": "EternaGym_Text_GardeniaExplainGrassKnot",
            "en_US": [
                "That {STRVAR_1 8, 0, 0} contains\n",
                "the move {STRVAR_1 6, 1, 0}.\r",
                "It\u2019s one of my favorite moves.\r",
                "The heavier the foe, the more\n",
                "damage this move will cause."
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": "EternaGym_Text_GardeniaGymBeaten",
            "en_US": [
                "Yup! If there\u2019s one thing I can tell\n",
                "about you, it\u2019s this!\r",
                "You and your Pok\u00e9mon are gonna get\n",
                "even tougher, and I mean seriously!"
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": "EternaGym_Text_LassCarolineBeforeBattle",
            "en_US": [
                "Welcome!\n",
                "Without further ado, let\u2019s go!\r"
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": "EternaGym_Text_LassCarolineAfterBattle",
            "en_US": [
                "This gym\u2019s floral clock...\n",
                "You can walk on its hands.\f",
                "That\u2019s how you get to the next Trainer."
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": "EternaGym_Text_AromaLadyJennaBeforeBattle",
            "en_US": [
                "My Grass-type Pok\u00e9mon can dole out\n",
                "some serious special attacks...\r",
                "I won\u2019t let you win...easily!\r"
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": "EternaGym_Text_AromaLadyJennaAfterBattle",
            "en_US": [
                "Every time you beat a Trainer, the\n",
                "floral clock moves.\r",
                "The fountain also stops if I lose.\r",
                "It\u2019s so you can go to the Pok\u00e9mon\n",
                "Center during your challenge."
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": "EternaGym_Text_AromaLadyAngelaBeforeBattle",
            "en_US": [
                "You can\u2019t win when you\u2019re distracted by\n",
                "the lovely aromas of Pok\u00e9mon!\r"
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": "EternaGym_Text_AromaLadyAngelaAfterBattle",
            "en_US": [
                "The floral clock moves, and time\n",
                "flows...\r",
                "There\u2019s only our Gym Leader left.\n",
                "Go on, don\u2019t be afraid!"
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": "EternaGym_Text_FountainWaterLevelDropped",
            "en_US": [
                "The fountain\u2019s water level dropped!\r",
                "It\u2019s possible to walk across the\n",
                "fountain now!"
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": "EternaGym_Text_GymGuideBeforeBadge",
            "en_US": [
                "Hey, there!\n",
                "How\u2019s it going, Champ-to-be?\r",
                "Actually, that\u2019s what I said to some\n",
                "boy who zipped in here earlier, too!\r",
                "The Gym Leader, Gardenia, is a user\n",
                "of Grass-type Pok\u00e9mon.\r",
                "It should be obvious, but Grass-type\n",
                "Pok\u00e9mon really hate fire.\r",
                "They\u2019re also at a huge disadvantage\n",
                "against the Flying type, too.\r",
                "Oh, wait a second. I should tell you\n",
                "about the Gym itself first.\r",
                "You can\u2019t challenge the Gym Leader\n",
                "until you beat all the Gym\u2019s Trainers.\r",
                "It\u2019s a bit challenging, but just think\n",
                "of it as good training and go for it!"
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": "EternaGym_Text_GymGuideAfterBadge",
            "en_US": [
                "Oh! {STRVAR_1 3, 0, 0}!\n",
                "You\u2019ve beaten the Gym Leader!\r",
                "Your Pok\u00e9mon look much tougher than\n",
                "when they went in, too!\r",
                "At least that\u2019s how I see it!"
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": "EternaGym_Text_GymStatueBeforeBadge",
            "en_US": [
                "Eterna City Pok\u00e9mon Gym\n",
                "Leader: Gardenia\r",
                "Certified Trainers:\n",
                "{STRVAR_1 3, 1, 0}"
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": "EternaGym_Text_GymStatueAfterBadge",
            "en_US": [
                "Eterna City Pok\u00e9mon Gym\n",
                "Leader: Gardenia\r",
                "Certified Trainers:\n",
                "{STRVAR_1 3, 0, 0}\f",
                "{STRVAR_1 3, 1, 0}"
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": "GymExit_Text_MustDefeatLeader_EternaGym",
            "en_US": [
                "You can\u2019t leave until you\n",
                "defeat the Gym Leader!\r"
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": "Blitz_Text_FifthBadgePower",
            "en_US": [
                "You now have 5 Gym Badges!\n",
                "In Blitz mode, these HMs\n",
                "are now available:\r",
                "Fly, Cut, Strength,\n",
                "Rock Climb, and Surf!"
            ]
        }
    ]
}